{"title":"Y-Mount Offers Strapless Saddlebag Mounting, For Most Seat Posts","link":"https://bikerumor.com/y-mount-strapless-saddlebag-mounting/","date":1720188000000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-hero.jpeg\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" alt=\"(Photos/Y-Mount)\" /></p>\n<p>Want to run a larger saddle bag without it being a floppy mess? Well, Y-Mount says they offer such a product. And at this year’s Eurobike, <a href=\"https://www.y-mount.de/\" target=\"_blank\">Y-Mount</a> launched their strapless saddlebag mount called, that’s right….the Y-Mount.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-with-saddlebag-e1720037225455.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"509\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-with-saddlebag-e1720037225455.jpeg\" alt=\"Y-Mount Strapless Saddlebag Mount with saddlebag\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-with-saddlebag-e1720037225455.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-with-saddlebag-e1720037225455-297x118.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-with-saddlebag-e1720037225455-120x48.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-with-saddlebag-e1720037225455-768x305.jpeg 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos/Y-Mount)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new <a href=\"https://www.y-mount.de/\" target=\"_blank\">Y-Mount</a> doesn’t just claim to offer strapless mounting, but it claims that it will eliminate that annoying “saddlebag sway”, no matter how large and heavily loaded the saddlebag is. They also claim that the Y-Mount weighs only 35g and will fit almost any bike. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-exploded-view.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-exploded-view.jpeg\" alt=\"Y-Mount Strapless Saddlebag Mount exploded view\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-exploded-view.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-exploded-view-297x167.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-exploded-view-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-exploded-view-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-exploded-view-1200x675.jpeg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-dimensions.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-dimensions.jpeg\" alt=\"Y-Mount Strapless Saddlebag Mount dimensions\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-dimensions.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-dimensions-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-dimensions-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-dimensions-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-dimensions-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-dimensions-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Let’s take a look at the details. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Two guys named Thomas and Simon were fed up with saddlebags that were attached via straps. After thinking of a universal and durable fixing point that could be found on almost every bike, they decided to mount to the seat rails at four separate, fixed points for ultimate strength. They applied for a patent, and the Y-Mount was born.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Y-Mount</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Because mount. Just kiddin’. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Y-mount is made of carbon fiber, claims to weigh in at a svelt 35g, and can be used for saddlebags, bottle holders, stabilizers, and mudguards. Also, the way the Y-Mount set up allows for the quick swap of bags and accessories.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here is a list of accessories that will be available around October.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Saddlebags 4L, 8L, and 13L</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-front-side-shot--e1720037322416.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1181\" height=\"870\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-front-side-shot--e1720037322416.jpeg\" alt=\"Y-Mount Strapless Saddlebag Mount front side shot\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-front-side-shot--e1720037322416.jpeg 1181w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-front-side-shot--e1720037322416-297x219.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-front-side-shot--e1720037322416-120x88.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-front-side-shot--e1720037322416-768x566.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Bottle Holder</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-bottle-mount-e1720037446238.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"669\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-bottle-mount-e1720037446238.jpeg\" alt=\"Y-Mount Strapless Saddlebag Mount bottle mount\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-bottle-mount-e1720037446238.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-bottle-mount-e1720037446238-297x155.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-bottle-mount-e1720037446238-120x63.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-bottle-mount-e1720037446238-768x401.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Stabilizer</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-stabalizer.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"729\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-stabalizer.jpeg\" alt=\"Y-Mount Strapless Saddlebag Mount stabalizer\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-stabalizer.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-stabalizer-297x169.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-stabalizer-120x68.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-stabalizer-768x437.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-stabalizer-with-bottle-mount.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"830\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-stabalizer-with-bottle-mount.jpeg\" alt=\"Y-Mount Strapless Saddlebag Mount stabalizer with bottle mount\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-stabalizer-with-bottle-mount.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-stabalizer-with-bottle-mount-297x193.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-stabalizer-with-bottle-mount-120x78.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-stabalizer-with-bottle-mount-768x498.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Garmin mount for Varia Radar</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-Garmin-mount-e1720037506559.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"488\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-Garmin-mount-e1720037506559.jpeg\" alt=\"Y-Mount Strapless Saddlebag Mount Garmin mount\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-Garmin-mount-e1720037506559.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-Garmin-mount-e1720037506559-297x113.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-Garmin-mount-e1720037506559-120x46.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-Garmin-mount-e1720037506559-768x293.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Mudguard</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-mudguard-e1720037571656.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"462\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-mudguard-e1720037571656.jpeg\" alt=\"Y-Mount Strapless Saddlebag Mount mudguard\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-mudguard-e1720037571656.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-mudguard-e1720037571656-297x107.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-mudguard-e1720037571656-120x43.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Y-Mount-Strapless-Saddlebag-Mount-mudguard-e1720037571656-768x277.jpeg 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Get on the mailing list for yours now. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.y-mount.de/\" target=\"_blank\">Y-mount.de</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/y-mount-strapless-saddlebag-mounting/\">Y-Mount Offers Strapless Saddlebag Mounting, For Most Seat Posts</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"19d0761abfe8588ced08392158342f3d4d3a99835483d7dd9d43e9f56a1f1bd6","category":"Cycling"}